description: Welcome to 734 East 2nd St Unit 3 East Side living at its finest! This sun-drenched top-floor 2 bed, 1.5 bath home offers vaulted ceilings, an open-concept layout, and two incredible outdoor spaces. Entertain with ease in the bright living area with fireplace and direct access to a back deck. Upstairs, enjoy a show stopping private roof deck with sweeping 360 views. Both bedrooms feature custom closets, and gleaming hardwood floors run throughout. Central air, in-unit laundry, and a prime walkability bring this offering full circle.
